        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream",
        "Idle"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，所以入口点是IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream指向Idle。那程序加载怎么设计？是直接Load Program到Loading状态，还是需要中间状态？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Idle",
        "Loading",
        "Load Program"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Loading之后需要验证程序有效性，所以Loading通过Program Loaded转换到Validating状态。验证通过才进入Ready，不通过要报错。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Loading",
        "Validating",
        "Ready",
        "Error",
        "Program Loaded",
        "Program Valid",
        "Invalid Program"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，Validating分叉：Program Valid到Ready，Invalid Program到Error。那Ready之后用户Start Program进入Running？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Ready",
        "Running",
        "Start Program"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，Running状态需要支持暂停和恢复，还要有Dress Required的处理——这是工业场景的设备维护需求。另外程序正常结束到Complete，然后Reset回Idle。",
      "elements_involved": [
