      "utterance": "我画一下：Running通过Pause Command到Paused，Resume Command返回Running；Dress Required触发Dressing，Dress Complete回到Running；Program End到Complete，再Reset回Idle。Error状态也需要能Clear Error回到Idle吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
